      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just... it doesn't feel like a victory. it feels like i'm just done. like i've looked at the map and there's nothing left but the exit. even the scenery feels empty now. if the trip is over, why keep traveling? there's no point in continuing the route if you've already seen the end.",
